                <h4>Detonation</h4><p>关键词：节奏、动作</p><p>发售日期：7月8日</p><p>复古节奏地牢，不过在本作中以躲避敌人为主。Steam 页面上提供了免费试玩链接，觉得不错可以花3块支持一下作者~</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Detonation9493Jm.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13974" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1103430/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>We Become What We Behold</h4><p>关键词：新闻舆论</p><p>发售日期：7月9日</p><p>一个讲述媒体舆论的小作品。你作为新闻记者，要拍点什么来引人关注呢？拍不到有意思的东西，那就加个偏激的标题！</p><p>追记：本作最早是免费公开发布的，但 Steam 平台的本作并非原作者授权上传，还请不要购买。感兴趣可以直接到 itch 上游玩支持（免费的）。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-We_Become_What_We_Behold0236Zl.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13975" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><div class="promo promo-border promo-white bottommargin topmargin"><h3>We Become What We Behold</h3><a class="button button-dark button-xlarge button-border button-rounded" href="https://ncase.itch.io/wbwwb" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><i class="icon-display"></i> 在线玩</a></div><h4>Come Back: Chapter 1</h4><p>关键词：解谜、冒险</p><p>发售日期：7月9日</p><p>用另一种方式讲述有关家庭暴力、解离性漫游症的一款作品。主角醒来后发现身处于陌生的海岸上，帮助他寻找并解开各种令人困惑的难题，了解背后令人痛苦的真相。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Come_Back10304si.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13976" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Come_Back20312TM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13977" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Come_Back30319YD.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13978" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1102510/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Godhood</h4><p>关键词：模拟、策略</p><p>发售日期：7月11日</p><p>创建属于你自己的宗教！在战略性上帝模拟游戏《Godhood》中指引、培养你的忠实信徒。决定他们的善恶美丑。鼓励教徒建造宏伟的庙宇，在那里举办仪式来歌颂你的荣光。转化信徒，击败对手，成为众神之王。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Godhood10704CU.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="14001" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Godhood20771dS.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="14002" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Godhood30779FY.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="14003" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/917150/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>FurryFury</h4><p>关键词：免费、弹珠、多人</p><p>发售日期：7月11日</p><p>弹珠互撞，击破敌人或者让敌人撞向陷阱！游戏支持多人联机。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-FurryFury1569Ys.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13979" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-FurryFury21596fn.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13980" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/906870/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>RED HOT VENGEANCE</h4><p>关键词：免费、双摇杆射击</p><p>发售日期：7月11日</p><p>将夜晚染上鲜血！游戏包含30+关卡，可定制武器，支持地图编辑器和创意工坊。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-RED_HOT_VENGEANCE4073JA.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13981" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1058640/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Blazing Chrome 炽热合金</h4><p>关键词：横向滚屏、射击、动作</p><p>发售日期：7月11日</p><p>机械统治着地球，活下来的少数人类也处在灭绝的边缘。在金属和电路组成的新统治者面前，人类失去了能源、地位和尊严。带上你最好的朋友和满满的子弹，射爆那堆废铜烂铁，解放人类同胞，体验子弹横飞的刺激和爽快吧！游戏支持中文，支持本地多人。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Blazing_Chrome153147R.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13982" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Blazing_Chrome25326nB.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13983" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/609110/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Professor Lupo and his Horrible Pets</h4><p>关键词：冒险、解谜</p><p>发售日期：7月11日</p><p>Nihilumbra 开发组新作。Lupo 教授是一位太空科学家，他收集了很多外星生物，这些生物仿佛人畜无害，但一旦觉察到身旁有人类，就会化为致命的怪物。Lupo 教授决定将这些生物当做武器贩卖，但这时，收容生物的空间站受到了神秘力量的攻击，怪物们逃了出来！</p><p>你作为 Lupo 教授的实习生，本职工作是充当这些生物的诱饵。在这个危机状况下，显然就是怪物们的一顿大餐！想尽一切办法逃离这里，揭开空间站背后的秘密和自己不为人知的身世与过去。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Professor_Lupo16241QW.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13984" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Professor_Lupo26261Ji.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13985" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Professor_Lupo36269H6.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13986" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/741520/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Eagle Island</h4><p>关键词：rogue-lite、动作</p><p>发售日期：7月12日</p><p>扮演 Quill 和他的猫头鹰伙伴 Koji 一起探索鹰之岛，探索失落文明，与古神对抗，拯救被抓走的小鸟 Ichiro！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eagle_Island6853CS.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13990" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eagle_Island16425jx.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13987" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eagle_Island26431et.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13988" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/681110/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Alien Escape</h4><p>关键词：益智、解谜</p><p>发售日期：7月12日</p><p>旋转重力，逃离这座困住你的要塞！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Alien_Escape7750E3.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13991" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1116290/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Spy Tactics</h4><p>关键词：策略、回合制</p><p>发售日期：7月13日</p><p>扮演执行秘密任务的特工，开锁、取得重要道具、消灭目标，一小步的判断出错可能会影响整个棋局！仔细观察敌人的行动模式，精打细算完成任务！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Spy_Tactics82838y.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13992" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Spy_Tactics28327RF.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13993" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Spy_Tactics38334Uf.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13994" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1073280/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>AvoCuddle</h4><p>关键词：动作、冒险</p><p>发售日期：7月13日</p><p>情侣间的一次吵架后，还没来得及和好，恋人就被飞碟绑架了！再多后悔不如立即行动，在星球之间冒险，拯救真爱！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-AvoCuddle18839kl.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13995" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-AvoCuddle28850O0.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13996" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-AvoCuddle38856ks.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13997" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1072610/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>其他值得关注的作品</h4><ul><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1097800/Stranger_Things_3_The_Game/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《怪奇物语3》</a></li><li>3D 平台跑酷游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1105620/Exertus/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Exertus</a></li><li>恐怖解谜 RPG <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/990020/SINNERS/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">SINNERS</a></li><li>SEGA《雷莎出击》精神续作 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/834800/SolSeraph/">SolSeraph</a> （塔防+平台动作）</li><li><a href="https://indienova.com/u/1000water" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">@千水</a> 团队的 Roguelike 塔防游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1054800/_/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《变量》</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1102100/TINY_METAL_FULL_METAL_RUMBLE/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《小小合金：虚构的帝国》</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1036440/Kingdom_Wars_2_Definitive_Edition/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《王国战争2：终极版》</a></li><li>快节奏多人 fps<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/555000/Goat_of_Duty/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《使命羊唤 Goat of Duty》</a></li><li>音符合成益智小游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1070250/NOTES/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">NOTES</a></li><li>火箭发射模拟游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1069030/EarthX/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">EarthX</a></li></ul>
            </div>
